Interface CommandPanel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Panel

    public interface CommandPanel
extends Panel
    A representation of the model object 'Command Panel'. Pannello destinato a contenere esclusivamente widget di comando (es. pulsanti).

    The following features are supported:

    • Cmd Style
    • Widgets
